  "description": "This image depicts the interior of a car wash, focusing on the overhead structure. The primary view is upwards towards the ceiling, showcasing a series of metal beams, a corrugated metal roof, and various equipment components. Two bright, rectangular lights are mounted on the beams, providing illumination for the washing process. A green, possibly copper, pipe runs horizontally across the frame, showing signs of corrosion. Several white and black hoses and cables hang from the ceiling, along with a cylindrical component. The background reveals the metal doors of the car wash bay, and some signage is partially visible. The overall scene suggests a functional, industrial environment designed for automated vehicle cleaning.",
